<plot>When Hayes' gang kill Jim Carter, Dodie Cameron finds his money and hides it. Failing to find the money and seeing Dodie Cameron nearby, the gang chases her only to be run off by Steve Randall. When they kidnap her to get her to talk, Steve breaks that up. But just as Steve is then recovering the money she hid, he is captured and arrested for the murder.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?423591</url></doc>
